    "First, we do not rely on costly annotations of training examples produced by commercial language models.",
    "Second, we enhance existing question-answering training datasets by incorporating instructions and merge data representing various tasks.",
    "This approach instructs the model to adapt dynamically and determine the most appropriate mechanism (either internal or tool-based) to address each specific query.",
